	CPT: Gopal Das, Rajib Rao, Ayeni Bademi Daniel, Tarun Kumar Prasad, Satyajit Dutta, Koushik Prasad, Avijit Ghosh, Sovan Das, Sanjit Saha (Sk. Hassanurujjaman 73), Ezehnna Henry, Rajib Ekka (Subhomoy Das 90).         
	Referee: Biplab Poddar.         
	Man of the Match: Peter Odafe.                                                                                                                          
